Architecture
============
Codebus
    a system that runs code in different programming languages
    return code output for a snippet
    return code results against test cases
Contesto
Playground

Code Run Flow
=============
Client sends code to the Codebus using a POST request
Codebus returns CUID (Code Unique ID) to the client
The client request status updates about CUID using websockets
When status changes, Codebus inform the client using websockets
